Stunning historic win for @GoSwords womens volleyball as they upset #1 Alaska Anchorage in the opening round of the @NCAADII tournament, avenging a preseason loss. @ThePacWest Newcomer of the year Sasha Colombo with a a match-high 20 kills.

full_text.1: 🏐 #SwordsVB upsets No. 1 seed Alaska Anchorage in 5 sets in first round of NCAA West Regional and will face 4th-seed Cal Poly Pomona in semis tomorrow. Four 'Swords w/ double-digit kills, led by Colombo's 20. Corti adds 17. #SwordsOhana #ChaminadeOnTheRise
